                <h1>Farmer urges Class of 2015 to develop empathy, dream big</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/39d133bb-e1b8-45f9-8ab4-6092029ec003.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="Despite&#x20;threats&#x20;of&#x20;inclement&#x20;weather,&#x20;commencement&#x20;2015&#x20;went&#x20;smoothly&#x20;at&#x20;the&#x20;Durham&#x20;Bulls&#x20;Athletic&#x20;Park&#x20;Sunday&#x20;morning." class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            Despite threats of inclement weather, commencement 2015 went smoothly at the Durham Bulls Athletic Park Sunday morning.

